The '''Chidinkalu''', '''Chidinkalu horn''', or '''Kitonak pipe''' was a [[Music/Legends|musical]] instrument made by the [[Kitonak/Legends|Kitonaks]] from the hollowed-out reeds of a [[chidinka]]. It produced low tones and was used in the rhythm section.

